The app uses Solid technology to allow people to build their own "personal online data repository", or PTD.
It can include contact lists, to-do lists, a calendar, a music library, and other personal and professional tools.
It is like if Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack and Spotify were all available at the same time in the same browser.
Personal online data storage is unique in that only the user determines who and what kind of information can be accessed.
