According to CEO John Bruce, the idea behind Inrupt is to provide the company with the resources, processes and skills to make Solid accessible to everyone.
The company currently includes Burners-Lee, Bruce, a security platform purchased by IBM, some freelance developers hired to work on the project, and a community of voluntary coders.
